Provides classes and interfaces for integrating MVEL into the Nomen project.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NameResolver
    An MVEL VariableResolver for resolving MVEL variables from a Named.
    NameResolverFactory
    A BaseVariableResolverFactory that produces NameResolver instances for use by MVEL expressions.
